posting_body: ['WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM EASY TO  QUALIFY!', 'Quick move in.', 'If you are an independent worker have low credit or background issues and have problems finding a place to settle with your family, do not hesitate call me or TEXT me, I am a rental expert in South Florida, I will find a property for you and get you approved.', 'WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM with credit score of over 550, we will buy any property CASH for you  up tp $600,000 and then rent it to you for 1 to 3 years until you can get ready to purchase it, it will save some of your rent money towards the purchase ( about 25% of payment).', 'Beautiful large and meticulously kept luxury home in quiet neighborhood.', 'One bedroom and full cabana bath downstairs.', 'Oversized primary suite with large en suite bath and two walk in closets.', 'Additional bedrooms upstairs share a conveniently accessible Jack and Jill bathroom.', "Chef's kitchen and laundry room with storage, newer model washer/dryer and utility sink.", 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'I RESPOND INMIDIATELLY!!', 'show contact info', ')', '""EASY SOLUTIONS REALTY LLC ""']
